nodes.text: This obstetrician assisted in the delivery of Jacen and Jaina Solo. He was the only organic medical practitioner present at the event, and was assisted by two MD-series droids.

In The Last Command this medic has dialogue but is not physically described, to the point of even omitting his gender. Conversely, in the comic adaptation he is depicted but has no dialogue, only giving a "thumbs-up" gesture. In both versions, the composition of the delivery room staff is the same.
